<lyrics>[V1]
 fy skwn wạlnạs nạỷmwn ạ̹lạ rʿạẗ yshrwn ʿly̱ qṭyʿ yḥrswn

[V2]
 fạ̹dẖạ nwr mn ạlʿlạ ybhr ạlʿywn bsẖrhm jnd ạlsmạʾ ạ̉yhạ ạlbnwn

[V3]
 qd wld ạlywm bynkm fy ạlạ̉rḍ rỷys llslạm hw ạlmsyḥ ạlrb

[V4]
 fy ạlsmạʾ ạlmjd slm ʿly̱ ạlạ̉rḍ frḥ lkl ạlnạs qd jạʾ ạlkẖlạṣ

[V5]
 sndẖhb ạ̹lyh ḥytẖmạ ykwn wnsjd ldyh nḥn kẖạsẖʿwn

[V6]
 bsẖry̱ mạ rậhạ ạ̹lạ ạlsạhrwn</lyrics>
